# Artifact-first architecture
- Every feature starts as an artifact specification.
- No code without a corresponding artifact.
- .axp pack format for deterministic distribution.

# Gate certification
- 9 gates, sequential. No gate may be skipped.
- Each gate has entry criteria, evidence, exit criteria.
- GATE9_CERTIFICATION.md is the master report.

# Build process
- Steps 0–9 with explicit exit criteria.
- Each step produces required artifacts.
- Deterministic: same input → identical .axp pack.

# Documentation
- ARTIFACT_FIRST.md is the primary development model.
- No spec drift: docs must match code.
- Evidence-required: no claims without proof.
